# 🐞 BR-001 - Login fails with valid credentials

## 📍 Environment
- Browser: Google Chrome (latest)
- OS: Windows 10/11
- Application: Demo e-commerce webshop

---

## 🧪 Steps to Reproduce
1. Open login page
2. Enter valid username
3. Enter valid password
4. Click on "Login" button

---

## ❗ Actual Result
User is not logged in. System displays an error message: "Invalid credentials".

---

## ✅ Expected Result
User should be successfully logged in and redirected to the dashboard/homepage.

---

## 📊 Severity
High

## 🎯 Priority
P1

---

## 📝 Notes
Issue is reproducible consistently.
